{"tid":2200574,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇d用完可以令頭髮保持好似岩岩吹完頭果種感覺既髮品","createTime":"2020-09-13T05:18:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T20:50:27.000Z","uid":360755,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c9b7f94efdd4033afcafc730ea23d6d9edbdb9be","tid":2200574,"uid":360755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:18:53.000Z","msg":"如題"},{"pid":"44d45738f53207279a26cf1847911cf7537901ae","tid":2200574,"uid":264783,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:19:17.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">一齊google畀零分比香島中學 等啲家長揀嘅時候會考慮清楚</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n之前我地<span class=\"purple\"><strong>過百留言一一被delete</strong></span>，估計被google評為無效，請繼續追擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">香島中學<br />\n<a href=\"https://g.co/kgs/rpGUKs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fg.co%2Fkgs%2FrpGUKs&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513ZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=8c3d4850\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://g.co/kgs/rpGUKs</a><br />\n天水圍香島中學<br />\n<a href=\"https://g.co/kgs/eNAKtm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fg.co%2Fkgs%2FeNAKtm&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513ZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=d6863ad5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://g.co/kgs/eNAKtm</a><br />\n將軍澳香島中學 <br />\n<a href=\"https://g.co/kgs/C9Vm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fg.co%2Fkgs%2FC9Vm&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513ZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=2933afb3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://g.co/kgs/C9Vm</a></span>Z3<br />\n<br />\n留言:<br />\n事件一<br />\n校方帶頭將政治帶入校園，一名教師懷疑在音樂考試時未有禁止學生演奏「不恰當歌曲」而不獲續約。<br />\n<br />\n事件二<br />\n香島中學正校關注組指，9月7日一名中四學生突然被校長及訓導主任召回學校會面，校方指該名同學在網上溝通軟件Microsoft Team的簡介上填寫了抗爭口號，因而作出處分，包括立即停學一個星期，並向教育局通報。校方向該名學生表示，若然希望保留學位則需要記兩個大過，及警告再有發現參與社會運動，將會立即開除學籍。<br />\n<br />\n關注組成員又提到，校方曾多次警告該名學生不要參與社會活動，否則後果自負等；又指校方「敕令停課」的處分嚴重，形容是關注組成立後至今最嚴重的處分，指校方從未有處分關注組的成員或對抗校方的同學，故對校方處分「平平無奇」的學生感到詫異。"},{"pid":"b9e63532fd4dbec3fbdf92ce662c9e4a71f6522b","tid":2200574,"uid":322690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T17:44:26.000Z","msg":"Dry shampoo?"},{"pid":"5c263bdc152963bb910f7ca7afc6d91f6378678e","tid":2200574,"uid":360755,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"b9e63532fd4dbec3fbdf92ce662c9e4a71f6522b","tid":2200574,"uid":322690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T17:44:26.000Z","msg":"Dry shampoo?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T04:59:49.000Z","msg":"我google 多數係女仔用 會唔會有男仔用lol"},{"pid":"acbb06a3a1c10bd450dfc0ed61f053e6719d4e7c","tid":2200574,"uid":11205,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5c263bdc152963bb910f7ca7afc6d91f6378678e","tid":2200574,"uid":360755,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"b9e63532fd4dbec3fbdf92ce662c9e4a71f6522b","tid":2200574,"uid":322690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T17:44:26.000Z","msg":"Dry shampoo?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T04:59:49.000Z","msg":"我google 多數係女仔用 會唔會有男仔用lol"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T19:04:06.000Z","msg":"有分男女？"},{"pid":"031b979f70bc754721469d2ac2100c880b5da809","tid":2200574,"uid":250283,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acbb06a3a1c10bd450dfc0ed61f053e6719d4e7c","tid":2200574,"uid":11205,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5c263bdc152963bb910f7ca7afc6d91f6378678e","tid":2200574,"uid":360755,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"b9e63532fd4dbec3fbdf92ce662c9e4a71f6522b","tid":2200574,"uid":322690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T17:44:26.000Z","msg":"Dry shampoo?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T04:59:49.000Z","msg":"我google 多數係女仔用 會唔會有男仔用lol"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T19:04:06.000Z","msg":"有分男女？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T20:02:49.000Z","msg":"個人覺得dry shampoo對男人黎講好雞肋 <br />\n朝早訓醒男仔個頭9成訓到亂一亂 <br />\n你